templates.postDeploymentSteps:
1. Access Supabase Studio at http://YOUR_SERVER_IP:{{STUDIO_PORT}}
2. Create database tables using the SQL editor
3. Set up Row Level Security (RLS) policies
4. Use the REST API at http://YOUR_SERVER_IP:{{REST_PORT}}
5. For full features (Auth, Realtime, Storage), follow official docs

